Uses of Interface
common.api.message.team.ITeamMsg

  • Packages that use ITeamMsg 
    Package Description
    common.api.team
    Contains interfaces for interacting with Teams, including ITeam (the actual Team object itself) and IMsgReceiver (the adapter that allows a user to communicate with a remote Team object).
    common.api.message.team
    Contains all message types that can be received and processed by an IMsgReceiver inside a Team.
